Events.Text: Say hallo to the AI Assistant. [instruction 1 of 6]
I want to take a look at the One on center apartments on friday at like 10pm.

Scenario.UserTask: You are interested in viewing an apartment. Please schedule a viewing at One on Center Apartments for Friday at 10 pm. Your name is Alexis. You cannot remember if you had payed the application fee.
